00:14:35,610 --> 00:14:36,350
Yes.

229
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:38,870
When you become successful,

230
00:14:38,870 --> 00:14:40,370
don't forget

231
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:42,620
us old friends from Shanglin Office.

232
00:14:42,620 --> 00:14:43,700
- Yes.
- Yes.

233
00:14:43,860 --> 00:14:44,410
Liangyuan.

234
00:14:44,780 --> 00:14:45,610
Don't forget

235
00:14:45,610 --> 00:14:46,810
our years of friendship.

236
00:14:47,140 --> 00:14:49,244
Our friendship is stronger than gold.

237
00:14:49,980 --> 00:14:50,660
Yes.

238
00:14:51,820 --> 00:14:52,980
I've been in Shanglin Office

239
00:14:53,020 --> 00:14:54,200
for half my life.

240
00:14:54,355 --> 00:14:56,133
I don't understand other principles.

241
00:14:56,155 --> 00:14:57,590
But I know

242
00:14:58,780 --> 00:15:01,940
