is grafted onto the peach tree.

243
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:05,044
The peach grows large if an apricot
is grafted onto the peach tree.

244
00:15:05,460 --> 00:15:06,460
But no matter what,

245
00:15:06,460 --> 00:15:07,340
it remains a peach.

246
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:10,650
Although I got
Right Chancellor's silver token,

247
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:12,200
I'm still

248
00:15:12,380 --> 00:15:13,260
Li Shande.

249
00:15:13,311 --> 00:15:14,355
Nothing has changed.

250
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:17,000
So I really can't take

251
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:17,890
your stuff.

252
00:15:18,220 --> 00:15:19,930
Take them back.
I really can't take them.

253
00:15:19,930 --> 00:15:20,720
Please go back.

254
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:23,240
Well, no wonder

255
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:26,150
your father can get things done.

256
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:30,020
