257
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:33,422
he's still
the same honest and good-hearted man.

258
00:15:33,444 --> 00:15:34,880
Yes.

259
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:38,060
Such integrity is admirable.

260
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:40,111
No wonder
Right Chancellor appreciates you.

261
00:15:42,410 --> 00:15:43,730
Please go back, Sirs.

262
00:15:46,870 --> 00:15:47,450
Well...

263
00:15:48,420 --> 00:15:50,420
Well...

264
00:15:50,420 --> 00:15:52,260
We'll leave you alone then.

265
00:15:52,260 --> 00:15:53,730
Yes, we'll leave you alone.

266
00:15:54,620 --> 00:15:55,020
Let's go.

267
00:15:55,020 --> 00:15:55,555
Alright.

268
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,830
Liangyuan, farewell.

269
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:02,950
Farewell.

270
00:16:20,030 --> 00:16:21,060
Follow up.

271
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:24,460
Coming.

