00:17:49,980 --> 00:17:50,940
You two get out.

292
00:17:52,380 --> 00:17:52,700
Yes.

293
00:17:53,020 --> 00:17:53,380
Yes.

294
00:18:02,860 --> 00:18:03,620
Chief Scribe Zhao.

295
00:18:05,260 --> 00:18:06,180
You don't need

296
00:18:06,180 --> 00:18:08,111
to be so jumpy.

297
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:10,460
We'll talk

298
00:18:11,700 --> 00:18:12,955
about your matter later.

299
00:18:14,860 --> 00:18:16,340
What matters most now

300
00:18:17,580 --> 00:18:18,660
is that Amita

301
00:18:18,955 --> 00:18:20,660
has already fled to Chang'an,

302
00:18:21,940 --> 00:18:24,133
far away from trouble.

303
00:18:24,380 --> 00:18:25,900
Why come back to Lingnan?

304
00:18:27,420 --> 00:18:29,000
Is she not afraid of death?

305
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:34,580
Does this

306
00:18:36,066 --> 00:18:38,866
have anything to do
with Right Chancellor?

307
00:18:42,740 --> 00:18:43,400
Inspector He.

308
00:18:44,777 --> 00:18:47,377
You're a local official
appointed by imperial decree.

309
00:18:47,900 --> 00:18:49,860
Even if Amita sowed discord

310
00:18:50,180 --> 00:18:51,866
between you and Right Chancellor,

311
00:18:51,940 --> 00:18:53,733
he would have
to go through official channels

312
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:56,140
to punish you.

313
00:18:57,460 --> 00:19:00,060
He needs to ask His Majesty

314
00:19:00,220 --> 00:19:01,100
to dismiss you

315
00:19:02,100 --> 00:19:04,500
before summoning you to the capital
to sentence you.

316
00:19:05,140 --> 00:19:07,220
There's no way he would only send

317
00:19:07,220 --> 00:19:09,377
these few people
to take punitive action against you.

318
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:11,300
Besides,

319
00:19:11,900 --> 00:19:13,380
Lingnan is your territory.

320
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:15,820
Now, you also

321
00:19:16,060 --> 00:19:17,220
hold the military tally.

322
00:19:17,940 --> 00:19:19,780
