officials' methods than we are.

330
00:19:44,866 --> 00:19:46,888
Corrupt officials are all the same.

331
00:19:47,380 --> 00:19:49,820
They all know when to turn a blind eye.

332
00:19:51,460 --> 00:19:53,220
Since the litchi transport

333
00:19:53,660 --> 00:19:54,933
is already a done deal,

334
00:19:55,060 --> 00:19:57,620
let Attendant Yu do whatever he wants.

335
00:19:58,020 --> 00:19:59,420
We just need to serve him well.

336
00:19:59,820 --> 00:20:01,460
He'll put in a good word for us

337
00:20:01,460 --> 00:20:02,955
in front of Right Chancellor.

338
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:05,340
If they really sent

339
00:20:05,340 --> 00:20:06,700
some rigid fool,

340
00:20:07,700 --> 00:20:08,980
who knows what would go wrong

341
00:20:08,980 --> 00:20:09,940
even if

342
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:12,288
Amita sowed discord.

343
00:20:16,740 --> 00:20:17,500
Anyway,

344
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:20,020
calculate their arrival time

345
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:23,666
and make proper arrangements.

346
00:20:26,380 --> 00:20:26,820
Yes.

