353
00:20:45,220 --> 00:20:46,820
When we start transporting the litchis,

354
00:20:46,820 --> 00:20:48,977
the weather might ruin things.

355
00:20:51,780 --> 00:20:53,740
I read your writing.

356
00:20:54,866 --> 00:20:56,700
It seemed alright on paper,

357
00:20:57,260 --> 00:20:59,460
but this entire trip

358
00:20:59,620 --> 00:21:01,900
made me think that transporting litchis

359
00:21:02,300 --> 00:21:03,688
is difficult.

360
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:06,060
But Mr. Li,

361
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:07,820
don't worry.

362
00:21:09,020 --> 00:21:10,380
We're assigned

363
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:11,740
by Right Chancellor this time.

364
