As long as we work together,

365
00:21:14,740 --> 00:21:16,220
there's nothing we can accomplish.

366
00:21:17,260 --> 00:21:18,300
We can ask

367
00:21:18,900 --> 00:21:20,060
Inspector's Office

368
00:21:20,666 --> 00:21:22,488
to help with operational matters.

369
00:21:22,666 --> 00:21:24,844
It's good enough
if they don't cause trouble.

370
00:21:27,180 --> 00:21:28,380
Do you

371
00:21:28,980 --> 00:21:30,700
have a grudge

372
00:21:31,377 --> 00:21:32,540
against Inspector's Office?

373
00:21:33,111 --> 00:21:35,222
It was just a minor misunderstanding.

374
00:21:36,060 --> 00:21:37,620
Yes, a minor...

375
00:21:38,222 --> 00:21:39,488
A minor misunderstanding.

376
00:21:40,540 --> 00:21:42,140
With Right Chancellor's silver token

377
00:21:42,220 --> 00:21:43,100
and your help,

378
00:21:44,340 --> 00:21:46,700
Inspector's Office might help us.

379
00:21:51,180 --> 00:21:52,260
When we get to Lingnan,

380
00:21:53,220 --> 00:21:54,660
let's go to Inspector He's place

381
00:21:55,740 --> 00:21:57,400
and have a good chat.

382
00:22:21,260 --> 00:22:23,540
Welcome to Lingnan,

383
00:22:23,600 --> 00:22:25,377
Inspector and Litchi Envoy!

384
00:22:33,340 --> 00:22:35,020
(Inspector's Office)

385
00:22:35,100 --> 00:22:36,488
Is it Inspector Yu?

386
00:22:43,860 --> 00:22:44,580
Inspector Yu.

387
00:22:49,666 --> 00:22:50,940
I've long heard about you.

388
00:22:51,460 --> 00:22:52,660
I didn't expect you

389
00:22:52,860 --> 00:22:55,500
to be so handsome, young, and promising.

390
00:22:56,060 --> 00:22:58,540
I heard you oversee

391
00:22:58,911 --> 00:23:00,140
the procurement and planning

392
00:23:00,180 --> 00:23:01,900
of Noble Consort's birthday banquet.

393
00:23:02,380 --> 00:23:03,060
Incredible.

394
00:23:04,220 --> 00:23:05,140
I'm honored

395
00:23:06,540 --> 00:23:07,780
to meet you today.

396
00:23:08,888 --> 00:23:11,860
I've heard of you for a long time.

397
00:23:13,140 --> 00:23:16,460
You ruled the seas back then.

398
00:23:17,460 --> 00:23:18,620
You dominated the sea

399
00:23:18,620 --> 00:23:20,020
with your brothers.

400
00:23:20,620 --> 00:23:21,380
Now,

401
00:23:21,820 --> 00:23:24,066
you became Lingnan's local magistrate,

402
00:23:24,700 --> 00:23:26,980
protecting the people.

403
00:23:27,940 --> 00:23:29,740
What a wonderful story.

404
00:23:32,060 --> 00:23:32,820
Inspector He.

405
00:23:34,500 --> 00:23:35,460
Actually,

406
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:39,180
I wanted to visit you for a long time,

407
00:23:40,100 --> 00:23:42,860
but I've been in the palace.

408
00:23:43,820 --> 00:23:46,740
We finally met.

409
00:23:47,220 --> 00:23:47,700
I

410
00:23:49,540 --> 00:23:50,929
must have a good chat

411
00:23:52,355 --> 00:23:54,660
about old times with you.

412
00:23:56,540 --> 00:23:57,620
Inspector Yu.

413
00:23:58,600 --> 00:24:00,740
Have we met before?

414
00:24:02,020 --> 00:24:03,940
You're concerned about Chang'an.

415
00:24:04,140 --> 00:24:05,340
Surely we've crossed paths

416
00:24:05,820 --> 00:24:07,060
in many matters.

417
00:24:07,860 --> 00:24:10,860
Maybe we met before.

418
00:24:11,700 --> 00:24:13,380
Look.

419
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:15,820
As soon as I saw you,

420
00:24:16,380 --> 00:24:17,740
I found you familiar.

421
00:24:18,300 --> 00:24:20,977
I feel like we've met before.

422
00:24:21,980 --> 00:24:23,740
Fate must have bound us long ago.

423
00:24:28,260 --> 00:24:29,060
Mr. Li.

424
00:24:35,333 --> 00:24:38,288
(Order of Tang's Duke of Wei)
Right Chancellor's silver token indeed.

425
00:24:41,500 --> 00:24:42,300
Mr. Li.

426
00:24:43,860 --> 00:24:44,977
As the old saying goes,

427
00:24:45,300 --> 00:24:48,100
a single day apart
feels as long as three autumns.

428
00:24:49,155 --> 00:24:51,111
We haven't seen each other
for so many days.

429
00:24:51,300 --> 00:24:53,140
How many autumns have passed?

430
00:24:55,420 --> 00:24:56,980
It's been a long journey.

431
00:24:56,980 --> 00:24:58,555
Don't worry about it.

432
00:25:07,060 --> 00:25:07,700
Amita.

433
00:25:09,580 --> 00:25:11,100
Since you left,

434
00:25:12,220 --> 00:25:13,620
I worry about you

435
00:25:14,020 --> 00:25:15,820
every day.

436
00:25:17,700 --> 00:25:20,088
Now all is well. You're back.

437
00:25:20,780 --> 00:25:21,780
My heart

438
00:25:22,140 --> 00:25:23,180
feels relieved.

439
00:25:24,220 --> 00:25:25,380
You have to promise me

440
00:25:26,180 --> 00:25:27,060
that you won't

441
00:25:27,060 --> 00:25:28,260
go so far anymore.

442
00:25:31,511 --> 00:25:32,955
Don't worry, Godfather.

443
00:25:33,940 --> 00:25:36,460
I don't plan to leave again this time.

444
00:25:42,044 --> 00:25:43,177
Where's Lan Yu?

445
00:25:43,540 --> 00:25:45,980
Why would I make things difficult
for a servant?

446
00:25:46,355 --> 00:25:47,311
I let her go.

447
00:25:47,911 --> 00:25:48,822
Inspector He.

448
00:25:52,500 --> 00:25:55,260
Please come here, Sirs.

449
00:25:57,460 --> 00:25:58,660
We prepared

450
00:25:58,900 --> 00:25:59,740
a few delicacies

451
00:26:00,380 --> 00:26:02,180
to welcome you.

452
00:26:02,940 --> 00:26:03,580
Yes.

453
00:26:04,540 --> 00:26:06,333
Hearing that you two are coming,

454
00:26:06,444 --> 00:26:08,088
we're eager to welcome you.

455
00:26:08,660 --> 00:26:10,820
I believe you two have seen

456
00:26:10,820 --> 00:26:12,500
Inspector He's raging enthusiasm.

457
00:26:13,820 --> 00:26:15,300
Let's discuss

458
00:26:15,580 --> 00:26:17,620
the litchi transport while we eat.

459
00:26:25,266 --> 00:26:27,444
There's a severe drought
in Longdong this year.

460
00:26:28,340 --> 00:26:30,980
His Majesty issued
a resource allocation edict,

461
00:26:31,111 --> 00:26:32,733
ordering civil and military officials

462
00:26:33,180 --> 00:26:34,700
to save public expenses.

463
00:26:37,620 --> 00:26:40,060
His Majesty
is considerate of the people.

464
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:42,100
To set an example for everyone,

465
00:26:43,340 --> 00:26:45,100
even the renovation of Huaqing Pond

466
00:26:46,955 --> 00:26:48,460
was stopped.

467
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:53,533
Wouldn't
such ostentatious but empty banquets

468
00:26:56,420 --> 00:26:57,340
go against

469
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:01,220
His Majesty's

470
00:27:01,220 --> 00:27:03,140
well-meaning intentions?

471
00:27:04,580 --> 00:27:06,888
You overstate it.

472
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:09,266
Lingnan is surrounded
by mountains and rivers.

473
00:27:09,288 --> 00:27:12,180
We have lots of fish and crabs.
Seafood is cheaper than rice here.

474
00:27:12,220 --> 00:27:13,860
We only prepared

475
00:27:14,060 --> 00:27:14,980
some Lingnan specialty

476
00:27:14,980 --> 00:27:16,555
home-cooked dishes.

477
00:27:16,740 --> 00:27:18,260
Inspector He is a local magistrate.

478
00:27:18,700 --> 00:27:19,980
Taking good care of you two

479
00:27:20,340 --> 00:27:22,622
will relieve His Majesty's worries.

480
00:27:22,740 --> 00:27:25,060
How could His Majesty blame him?

481
00:27:31,340 --> 00:27:32,060
Inspector He.

482
00:27:33,700 --> 00:27:35,133
Don't blame me.

483
00:27:35,500 --> 00:27:36,020
I'm

484
00:27:37,100 --> 00:27:38,700
impatient.

485
00:27:39,620 --> 00:27:42,666
When I think
of Noble Consort's upcoming birthday,

486
00:27:42,740 --> 00:27:44,500
the first thing I thought

487
00:27:44,780 --> 00:27:46,460
is to do a good job

488
00:27:46,660 --> 00:27:48,911
with the litchi transport.

489
00:27:49,060 --> 00:27:50,460
Of course.

490
00:27:50,860 --> 00:27:51,620
Yes.

491
00:27:52,540 --> 00:27:55,660
Since I'm an inspector,

492
00:27:56,940 --> 00:27:58,220
I must provide good service

493
00:27:58,700 --> 00:27:59,980
to Mr. Li.

494
00:28:00,740 --> 00:28:01,300
Mr. Li.

495
00:28:02,220 --> 00:28:03,500
If you have any requests,

496
00:28:04,460 --> 00:28:05,977
how about you ask them now?

497
00:28:06,020 --> 00:28:07,060
I'll go ahead then.

498
00:28:07,940 --> 00:28:09,660
The 1st day of June is coming.

499
00:28:09,900 --> 00:28:11,844
We must set off
on the 19th day of May!

500
00:28:12,460 --> 00:28:14,700
Please gather all the officials

501
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:16,288
to make arrangements in advance.

502
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:21,700
Inspector He.

503
00:28:23,600 --> 00:28:24,866
What do you think?

504
00:28:31,900 --> 00:28:32,340
Yes.

505
00:28:33,460 --> 00:28:35,488
Time waits for no one.

506
00:28:36,780 --> 00:28:38,580
Listen carefully. From today onward,

507
00:28:39,060 --> 00:28:40,420
all of Lingnan's officials

508
00:28:41,940 --> 00:28:43,666
shall obey Mr. Li's orders.

509
00:28:44,580 --> 00:28:45,620
- Yes.
- Yes.

510
00:28:49,777 --> 00:28:50,822
Speaking of,

511
00:28:51,940 --> 00:28:55,711
Amita is the Hu merchant representative
appointed by Right Chancellor.

512
00:28:56,620 --> 00:28:57,980
I wonder what Amita's plan

513
00:28:58,540 --> 00:28:59,933
is for this trip.

514
00:29:01,820 --> 00:29:02,460
Inspector Yu.

515
00:29:03,220 --> 00:29:05,100
Amita is my goddaughter.

516
00:29:05,820 --> 00:29:07,844
She has always been working for me.

517
00:29:08,088 --> 00:29:09,733
I lived in Lingnan for a long time.

518
00:29:09,866 --> 00:29:12,600
Every year, besides paying enough taxes

519
00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:14,755
to the court on time,

520
00:29:14,755 --> 00:29:16,750
I always ask myself

521
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:19,755
if I can do more.

522
00:29:20,260 --> 00:29:21,780
I'm afraid of failing His Majesty

523
00:29:22,220 --> 00:29:24,666
and Right Chancellor's trust in Lingnan.

524
00:29:25,100 --> 00:29:25,820
That's why

525
00:29:26,460 --> 00:29:28,977
I asked Amita to take on this job.

526
00:29:29,140 --> 00:29:30,900
It's also to make us

527
00:29:30,980 --> 00:29:32,380
work harder

528
00:29:33,100 --> 00:29:34,540
and give full support

529
00:29:34,660 --> 00:29:36,060
to the litchi transport.

530
00:29:37,300 --> 00:29:40,533
Yes, Godfather always said

531
00:29:40,550 --> 00:29:41,730
he wants to fund the transport

532
00:29:41,733 --> 00:29:43,600
in the name of Hu Merchants' Association

533
00:29:43,733 --> 00:29:45,377
to relieve His Majesty's worries

534
00:29:45,860 --> 00:29:47,888
and bring joy to Noble Consort.

535
00:29:50,820 --> 00:29:53,300
I must ask

536
00:29:53,733 --> 00:29:56,180
whether the money
funded by Hu Merchants' Association

537
00:29:56,540 --> 00:29:57,780
is an investment

538
00:30:00,220 --> 00:30:01,340
or a gift?

539
00:30:05,266 --> 00:30:06,900
Hu Merchants' Association has flourished

540
00:30:06,980 --> 00:30:08,620
in Tang under His Majesty's generosity.

541
00:30:09,260 --> 00:30:10,933
This money is of course a gift.

542
00:30:14,980 --> 00:30:16,940
Good.

543
00:30:19,660 --> 00:30:20,380
I

544
00:30:20,620 --> 00:30:22,340
didn't expect Hu Merchants' Association

545
00:30:22,460 --> 00:30:24,244
to be so generous.

546
00:30:24,780 --> 00:30:28,000
You contributed both money and manpower

547
00:30:28,460 --> 00:30:31,420
to the litchi transport.

548
00:30:31,977 --> 00:30:35,133
I have nothing to worry about anymore.

549
00:30:41,311 --> 00:30:42,800
Inspector He, please forgive us.

550
00:30:43,460 --> 00:30:45,020
The two envoys have traveled for days

551
00:30:45,088 --> 00:30:46,244
and are a little tired.

552
00:30:46,380 --> 00:30:48,500
How about you talk another day?

553
00:30:50,340 --> 00:30:51,060
Inspector Yu.

554
00:30:52,660 --> 00:30:55,577
Are you really not eating this meal?

555
00:30:56,220 --> 00:30:56,900
No need.

556
00:30:57,555 --> 00:30:58,355
Alright.

557
00:31:00,755 --> 00:31:01,800
Speaking of,

558
00:31:01,940 --> 00:31:03,580
I have a vacant courtyard.

559
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:05,980
Why don't you stay there

560
00:31:06,380 --> 00:31:07,688
