562
00:31:11,140 --> 00:31:13,340
Mr. Li, why don't you

563
00:31:15,220 --> 00:31:16,444
stay there?

564
00:31:17,780 --> 00:31:18,955
I'll go back to the inn.

565
00:31:18,977 --> 00:31:20,510
I'm familiar with the inn.

566
00:31:22,220 --> 00:31:22,660
Godfather.

567
00:31:23,533 --> 00:31:25,733
Right Chancellor
sent me to assist Mr. Li.

568
00:31:26,580 --> 00:31:28,088
I need to do everything myself.

569
00:31:28,540 --> 00:31:29,420
I'll stay at the inn

570
00:31:29,420 --> 00:31:30,466
with Mr. Li.

571
00:31:33,666 --> 00:31:34,377
Alright.

572
00:31:39,780 --> 00:31:41,000
Inspector Yu.

573
00:31:43,866 --> 00:31:44,911
Inspector He.

574
00:31:46,500 --> 00:31:47,100
Farewell.

575
00:31:47,700 --> 00:31:48,220
Farewell.

576
00:31:49,780 --> 00:31:51,260
Yu Cheng'en

577
00:31:52,580 --> 00:31:54,777
